<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>StackOverflow Preferred Answer</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #F0F6FF;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #FFFFFF;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #0077CC;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      p {
        margin: 1em 0;
      }
      a {
        color: #0077CC;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>StackOverflow Preferred Answer</h1>
      <p>Dear <%= displayName %>,</p>
      <p>Congratulations! Your answer on StackOverflow has been marked as the preferred answer.</p>
      <p>This means that your answer was the most helpful to the person who asked the question, and it will be displayed at the top of the list of answers.</p>
      <p>We want to thank you for your valuable contribution to the community. Your knowledge and expertise have helped countless people find solutions to their coding problems.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or feedback, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
      <p>Happy coding!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The StackOverflow Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
